@startuml
title Bilateral and triparty collateral management (colr business area)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #EEF5FF
  BorderColor #4A78B5
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #F7FAFF
  BorderColor #4A78B5
}
skinparam ArrowColor #4A78B5

package "Bilateral exchange" {
  [Party A\n(exposed, calls margin)] as A
  [Party B\n(posts collateral)] as B
}

package "Triparty service" {
  [Triparty agent\n(custodian / CSD)] as T
}

A --> B : colr.003 MarginCallRequest
B --> A : colr.004 MarginCallResponse
B --> A : colr.007 CollateralProposal
A --> B : colr.008 CollateralProposalResponse
A --> T : colr.019 Triparty instruction
T --> A : colr.022 Report / colr.023 Advice
note bottom of T : Party B instructs the agent\nand is reported to symmetrically
@enduml
